Date: Wed, 23 Dec 2020 10:40:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] RISC-V: Initial DTS for Microchip ICICLE board
Patch-mainline: Queued in openEuler repo, version 5.10.0-1.0.0
References: openEuler-21.03
